The Travelocity Gnome is looking for a new travel companion—you! Introducing the new Travelocity Gnome AR experience, now you can add a virtual gnome to your vacation photos and videos in real time, then spice them up with frames, weather effects, and travel props. Share your photos with family and friends via Instagram now too!

Just tap the banner that says “Roam with the Gnome” to get started!
